Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Yuueisha

Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.99,0:00:04.45,Main,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:05.15,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.53,0:00:09.78,Main,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,This Takagi-Mashiro team has gotten way better since the name stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:11.49,Main,Kimu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I really thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:13.58,Main,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,This thing's quite interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:15.25,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:18.38,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,For the early report, we're first!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:19.74,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! {Was all caps, made it lower-case.  Keep/revert?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:22.05,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,But don't get relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.05,0:00:23.97,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,You two have thirty-three votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.97,0:00:25.58,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-kun has thirty-one votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:30.18,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Hattori guy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:33.93,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Eiji loses, it will definitely put a damper on our serialization.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:36.80,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, there's no way Niizuma Eiji will lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.69,0:00:40.14,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I just got the results for the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:42.64,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Your rank for the real deal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:46.48,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Third place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.49,0:00:48.69,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Third?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:50.90,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-kun, you got first place in the questionnaires.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:52.16,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:55.03,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,What are questionnaires?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:59.37,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can make the character designs for serialization even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.63,0:01:01.54,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I can probably go with this protagonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:04.08,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:08.72,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,This boy doesn't need to know about the questionnaires and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:12.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:14.06,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of people who do mainstream,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.06,0:01:15.89,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,so being number one is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:18.64,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, doing cult is just running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:20.98,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What we're aiming for is number one in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{Opening}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.40,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:57.41,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:03:00.70,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you say, but why are you going so far for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:03.28,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. Just make sure you don't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.08,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.46,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Boxing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.63,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's mixed martial arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:09.58,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.51,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We're not playing around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:16.10,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:17.17,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:36.24,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,S–Stop it, I give, I give!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:45.92,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Shuujin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:47.88,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You get beat up by Miyoshi again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:49.37,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,No, I asked her to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:55.47,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I didn't understand the feelings of people who fight in battle stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:57.97,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that kind of different?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.63,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe you have a point...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:01.93,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Did you learn anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:04.06,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.14,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That's really the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:09.77,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We can't make a story about a protagonist who's afraid of fighting, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:15.31,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou-kun, congratulations on placing third in Jack NEXT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:18.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,If it were the main magazine, it would be a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:20.12,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But getting that rank in NEXT! has no meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:20.99,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.41,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:24.46,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What we're going for is first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:27.12,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, it's not enough to get us serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.91,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that may be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:30.63,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:35.26,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, everything in the world has ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.55,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:41.51,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,So, Saikou, why are you drawing Dragon Ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.18,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that someone else's manga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:44.26,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to copy it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:47.52,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to find scenes I scenes that stood out in ten battle manga... {QC: Shorten! :O}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:50.39,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,and copy at least a hundred pages from each.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.27,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred pages each from ten works?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:55.48,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't even do this much, I don't think I'll be able to draw a battle manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:58.24,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Doing this will help me make my own original drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:04:58.98,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:02.54,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's kind of hard to explain, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:07.08,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, what we did for NEXT! was a cult type manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:08.75,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We thought that to get first in Jack,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.63,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,we need to do a mainstream battle manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.34,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So, we're going to try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:15.92,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get what you mean about this mainstream and cult stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:19.34,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,But that's why Mashiro is studying Dragon Ball's artwork
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.84,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,and why you asked me to fight you seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:23.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.60,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really learn much from it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:28.80,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:32.56,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,How can you face forward and head straight for your dreams like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:33.94,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:37.23,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,About how in the second year of middle school, I went all the way to the national championships for karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:40.53,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,But I knew there were tons of people there stronger than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:43.82,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,and I also had exams to take, so I quit pretty easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:49.28,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Even Miho keeps trying and doesn't get discouraged when she fails an audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:52.13,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,So, Azuki failed some auditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.34,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.63,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't get an email about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:55.79,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I never got one like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.25,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:02.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't send her an email about getting third, which wasn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:04.13,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Azuki will only tell me when she overcomes hurdles...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:07.68,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,and gets closer to her dream, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.39,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That seems like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:13.31,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Miho sure is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:16.78,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Most girls, when they fail or feel down,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:19.40,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,want to be encouraged by the person they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:22.16,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to send Azuki a quick email.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:23.87,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:26.12,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,To tell her that the results from NEXT! weren't good this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:29.00,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm using it as motivation to try harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.04,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,So, you do have some sense in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:33.58,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,That will definitely encourage Miho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:36.05,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, send!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:47.77,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:49.10,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Miho's reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:52.35,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,They're short, but when they write to each other, they're always fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:53.76,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What did Miho say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:57.52,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,"Kaya told Mashiro to do something unnecessary, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:07:01.49,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her I said, 'Stop talking so indiscreetly!'"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:03.28,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. She found me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.23,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Azuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.79,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous of you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.45,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I want a dream, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.54,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you could do karate again or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:13.62,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like combat sports anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.45,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I want a more girlish dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:20.51,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll never be as good as you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:21.83,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I have no good features.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:27.81,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You're a nice person, Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:29.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You've got big tits, Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:32.18,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the way you look at me, Takagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.65,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What Mashiro said was way better!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:37.69,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, well you're a girl, so having a big chest is a good feature!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:39.73,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't talking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:42.10,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you total pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:42.90,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,You lech! {TLC?  Wtf?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:41.57,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreams, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:08.76,Main,Yoshida,0000,0000,0000,,Yuujirou, Niizuma Eiji will be starting YELLOW HIT in issue 33.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:09.39,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:12.39,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My luck is finally turning around.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:19.81,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does he have the music blasting again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:23.15,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told him several times that the serialization meeting was today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.77,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go have a meeting with Niizuma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.66,Main,Kimu,0000,0000,0000,,He's just lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.87,Main,Kimu,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma had been submitting works for the Tezuka Award for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:33.24,Main,Kimu,0000,0000,0000,,and he was just the first one to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:40.17,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-kun! Niizuma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:42.17,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,NIIZUMA-KUN!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:43.21,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.63,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's cool how you always suddenly appear like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:46.63,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Turn down the volume!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.38,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you to keep your phone nearby so you can answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:52.51,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:55.34,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,You can just leave your cell phone in a place you can see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.23,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,When you get a call, it will light up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:03.23,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with what's on my desk! Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:04.99,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,I–I got it, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.40,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What're you drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.11,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,It just hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.16,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:10.78,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Kitchen trash,{\alpha&HFF&} kitchen trash, combustible traaaash...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:11.24,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Kitchen trash, kitchen trash,{\alpha&HFF&} combustible traaaash...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.24,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Kitchen trash, kitchen trash, combustible traaaash... {Are these three lines lagging behind, or is it just me?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.16,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Don't draw stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.83,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Here, YELLOW HIT's serialization was decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.46,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Serialization?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:22.09,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,All right! All right! All right-pin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:23.55,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to be serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:24.38,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:26.01,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be the most popular author!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:27.17,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,C–Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.25,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.80,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's actually happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.89,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then don't make it so hard for me to get in contact with you, dammit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:35.02,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Also starting is Takano-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.93,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,You're going first, starting with issue 33.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:38.09,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,The ending manga are..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:39.76,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,When is my deadline?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:42.90,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting issue 33, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.07,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,for the color pages, it's the third of June.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:48.40,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,The center color page for chapter two, plus the rest of the chapter, are due on the thirteenth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:49.95,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Easy peasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.45,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Crowy cawy. {He's making a stupid kiddy rhyming thing here. If you didn't get it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:52.94,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll come to pick it up then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.37,0:09:56.25,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are still a bunch of things, like assistants...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:57.28,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:05.80,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this is good for a protagonist?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.33,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.51,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:12.05,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,next, similar to Ishinomori-sensei's "Kamen Rider"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.43,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,or Hara-sensei's "Hokuto no Ken",
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:16.43,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I was going for a dramatic battle story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.43,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I said this was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:20.85,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the name...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:21.73,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.40,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a world where demons run rampant,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.53,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there is a sword in which many demons dwell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:32.11,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The protagonist is the only human who can wield that sword without giving into its evil magic power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.27,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He defeats demons that try to steal the sword.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:36.54,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One demon appears from inside the sword,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:38.45,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}which he must also defeat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.42,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the sword is stolen, the world will be taken over by the demons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:44.71,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he defeats all the demons dwelling inside the sword,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:46.38,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the world will be at peace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.97,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should try to stay with swords, like we decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:52.30,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Then I got the idea to have the sword be the main part of the setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:53.67,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So honestly, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:58.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It kind of feels old.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:11:00.18,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like it's an idea that's been done to death...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:03.65,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's all right to do this sort of cliché setup for a mainstream story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:08.07,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,The problem will be how the story plays out and how we show the battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.40,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I think we have to bring it and show it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:14.03,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:21.45,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:23.75,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for having to meet at the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:25.04,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.41,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.62,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of feel pathetic though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:33.80,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Being an assistant to a sensei who's only in the second year of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.09,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:38.67,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,If you're upset about it, just try to get your own work serialized faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:40.97,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai-san, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:43.09,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm twenty-one, but how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.05,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty-three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:46.44,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:48.10,Main,Nakai,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.19,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are we starting today? Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:55.41,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:58.07,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he's done all of chapter one by himself already...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:01.95,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Then he doesn't need us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.57,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's still chapter two and past that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:05.71,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,At worst, you can meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:08.34,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Also, he's kind of a strange kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:10.29,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,so you're better off getting used to him as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:12.05,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Strange kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:16.84,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I have to get the color pages and go right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.55,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll give you a good introduction, so relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.55,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:24.98,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't your new series, "YELLOW HIT"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:26.55,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,What you did for NEXT! is "CROW", isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.69,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Serialize that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:30.43,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I finished the first chapter with sixty-four pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.53,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:36.02,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:38.41,Main,Mashiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori-san, you said that in three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:40.53,Main,Mashiro,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to compete with mainstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.49,Main,Mashiro,0000,0000,0000,,You never intended to serialize the cult story...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.70,Main,Mashiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Kono Yo wa Kane to Chie" in the first place, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.04,Main,Mashiro,0000,0000,0000,,So starting now, we're doing mainstream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:50.09,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you that you would get popular without doing mainstream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:51.79,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,No, we want to do mainstream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:55.29,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th–This is crazy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.64,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:14.52,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, lots of newcomers come in that have drawn mainstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:16.36,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Or, well, it's not that they come in thinking it's mainstream,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.61,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,it's just all they're exposed to are games and mainstream manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.28,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's all they can draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:22.78,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,But Takagi-kun can write stories that aren't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:23.66,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,That's your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:26.37,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality, what's popular in Jack are things like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.12,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Bleach,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.17,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Hunter X Hunter,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:29.00,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:30.04,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:31.50,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,all mainstream battle manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:35.96,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,You are ten years too early to be comparing yourselves to popular serialized manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:39.68,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,First, you should be thinking about what kind of manga you can get serialized, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.76,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,After all that effort, you got third in NEXT!,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.30,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,that's why I said you should stay on the road you're already on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.60,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But getting third in NEXT! won't carry us to serialization, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.40,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.69,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,If, in the next issue of NEXT!, you get the top spot for a newcomer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:54.19,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,third or better overall,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:56.19,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,and get within the top eight as a one-shot in the main magazine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:58.45,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about moving it toward serialization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:02.11,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,However, you two can't get popular with mainstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:04.78,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,This name isn't interesting at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.75,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:15.87,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,we'll think up and bring in a mainstream manga you think is good enough to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.55,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shuujin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.43,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Takagi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:25.40,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you, doing mainstream isn't the best way for you to utilize your talents and get popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:26.30,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:29.52,Main,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori-san is having a rare bout of anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:31.59,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's because they're promising newcomers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:33.03,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,Ashirogi Muto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:34.99,Main,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think they're promising?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:38.64,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes. I'm more of an Ashirogi fan than Niizuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:41.38,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's the "editor-approved, reader-rejected" types I'm uneasy about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:43.36,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,but not with the readers in general, so I'm a bit uneasy, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.73,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:47.40,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.76,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you finally made an excellent setup for a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:52.63,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,We should be talking about how to make use of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:54.65,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll do a good setup for mainstream—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:55.40,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:58.08,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma Eiji's manuscript for his new series won't be done in time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.01,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Niizuma Eiji?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:01.25,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}New series?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:02.81,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:05.66,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,You were just going to get the color pages and the finished chapter...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:07.04,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,with time to spare, weren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:10.33,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,What he was drawing wasn't his new series!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:14.86,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he was drawing the first chapter for "CROW", not "YELLOW HIT"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:17.06,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,"CROW"?! The hell! What are we going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:19.03,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,It's two days before the deadline for the color pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:20.28,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,There are nine days until it goes to print,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:23.62,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,so I asked if he could draw it in time, but he refuses to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:24.86,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't want to draw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:26.55,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,He can't just not draw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:29.07,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,We've never had a hole for new serialization in the entire history of the magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:30.97,Main,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Heishi, let me have the phone for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.24,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.28,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm putting the editor-in-chief on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.40,Main,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:39.62,Main,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Please bring the manuscript he did draw, along with Niizuma-kun himself, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:44.68,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,The editor-in-chief just told him to bring Niizuma Eiji here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:48.35,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma Eiji coming here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:52.55,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-kun, we're going to the editorial department.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:56.01,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to go to the Jack editorial department.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:01.70,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does he not understand what he's done?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:02.82,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:06.68,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I become the number one most popular author in Jack,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:11.52,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}please give me the power to end one manga that I hate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:13.49,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's the kind of kid who'd say something like that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:16.21,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no idea what he's thinking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:19.16,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I'm going to be this kid's editor, I can't be half-hearted about it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.99,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit, I was too naive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:25.77,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-kun, where's the manuscript you did for the first chapter of "CROW"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.84,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're standing on it, Yuujirou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:34.05,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:33.22,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.05,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,That's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.17,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:42.45,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they'll let me quit being an assistant here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:45.53,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-kun, answer me honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:48.45,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,If you have assistants, how many days will it take you to do sixty-four pages?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:50.20,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to draw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:53.86,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Crow's rival is discovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:55.61,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you want to draw it or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.84,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking if you did draw it, how many days would it take?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.25,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had assistants before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:04.07,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,If I had four days, I think that would be plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:05.08,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,How many?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:09.54,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? If the editorial department tells him to just shut up and draw, everything will be fine?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:13.46,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, from how he's been acting, he probably won't be any easier on the editor-in-chief.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:17.24,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the place? It sure is a pretty building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:18.71,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:20.34,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,I brought Niizuma-kun with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.31,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, sure is big.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:26.20,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where Jack gets made?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:33.03,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That's the genius...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.75,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma Eiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.81,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:40.38,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,I should have kept a better eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.37,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,He can't concentrate with people around,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.87,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,and whenever I called him on the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:45.38,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,he always just said he was doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:48.50,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,But when I asked him just now in the taxi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.17,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,he said that if he starts now, he could make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.26,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,Then hurry up and have him get drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:56.26,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, he says that he doesn't want to draw "YELLOW HIT" anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.23,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,So what if he doesn't want to draw it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:59.84,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,It was decided in the serialization meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.61,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,How can he be so selfish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:05.25,Main,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuujirou, let me see that manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:06.46,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:13.55,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,They've already decided to serialize Niizuma-san, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:15.40,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.63,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Should I have? {Would you have preferred I did?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.44,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to hide it or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:23.08,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we would want you to tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:24.45,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,He's our rival, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:26.92,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rival, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:30.38,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, coming from these two, that's how it is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.73,Main,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Did you read this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:40.20,Main,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:41.09,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.42,Main,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,"CROW" got first place in NEXT!, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:46.81,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:49.52,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,It actually got the majority of the votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.56,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,The first newcomer to do so in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:54.45,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying we should serialize this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:58.96,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,Editor-in-Chief, the preview at the end of issue 32 for "YELLOW HIT" has already been printed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:01.79,Main,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take responsibility for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:03.49,Main,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,With the idea of doing "CROW" in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.65,Main,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,are the names for chapters two and beyond made?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:08.29,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... No, I'll have to ask the author himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.20,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.65,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where did Niizuma-kun go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:16.10,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This all happened because of him, and yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:18.64,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:21.40,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Like I thought, you're Ashirogi Muto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:24.66,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I thought "Kono Yo wa Kane to Chie" was the most interesting one,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.10,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,is that getting serialized?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:27.18,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:29.03,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:31.20,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I could never come up with something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.02,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,It was incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.89,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The natural... genius?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:37.53,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he making fun of us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:39.76,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-kun, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:36.38,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,You're a two-man team, so that's how your story and drawings were both so deep. {This is barely audible. It's based on the manga. There's enough audible to tell he's saying the same thing.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:43.77,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,These two are the ones who wrote "Kono Yo wa Kane to Chie".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:45.78,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I love that manga, I'm their fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:50.80,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's only by one year,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:53.70,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,but the fact that you're younger than me and could draw that is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:56.05,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm really happy to hear you're close to my age!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:59.71,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I would really like to be comrades, working in Jack together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:04.45,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Aomori, so I don't have any friends my age here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:05.93,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be friends, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.41,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Working together?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:09.68,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Comrades?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.63,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be friends?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:13.39,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, he's not making fun of us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:14.97,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's being serious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:17.36,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. We can have a proper introduction later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:20.53,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,But first, did you do a name for chapters two and three of "CROW"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:23.20,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,If you did, then they might be okay with serializing "CROW".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:25.94,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll serialize "CROW".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:27.72,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,So you have the names? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:29.05,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,If they're at your apartment, we can go get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.64,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,They're in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:32.33,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use for them in your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:34.46,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:36.32,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,If you give me an hour, I can put them on paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:37.44,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,In one hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:39.92,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter two is twenty-five pages and chapter three is twenty-one pages!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:43.19,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I've already got them in my head, so it won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:44.50,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,CROW!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:46.04,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, over there, not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:48.11,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be in the way of the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:51.00,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,No, if you wouldn't mind, I'd like him to draw it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:56.73,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:20:58.21,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,O–Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:08.03,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You two, if you watch Niizuma Eiji,{\i0} {The word "this" is in there, but it's not necessary, right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.02,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you'll understand that you don't stand a chance doing mainstream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:13.15,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have to realize that you shouldn't be starting a mainstream battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.71,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:32.56,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:35.10,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't even thirty minutes, let alone an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:38.58,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring this over to the editor-in-chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:39.95,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,You come, too, Niizuma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:41.19,Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:46.44,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I think you've got a good grasp on what just happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:47.52,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:52.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,The series from NEXT! that's getting serialized, "CROW", is a mainstream battle manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:55.86,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma-kun is a genius-type.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:59.08,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you do mainstream, you won't be able to beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:00.59,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And it's the general viewpoint of the editorial department...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:04.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,that Niizuma-kun won't be able to become number one in the main magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:08.00,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be sure we won't win against Niizuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.00,0:22:08.91,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:11.95,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Our mainstream won't even be appearing together with Niizuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:15.51,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing your name today, I can tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:16.59,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,To be exact, you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.16,0:22:19.43,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,"I can tell you can't win based on this name."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.43,0:22:20.54,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.13,0:22:32.26,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.26,0:22:33.62,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Half a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:37.02,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't make a name that I approve of in half a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:39.17,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,you will follow my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.46,0:22:41.16,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,And then if you still insist on doing mainstream,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:43.54,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll step down as your editor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:45.06,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.69,0:22:46.71,Main,Ashirogi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:16.99,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Our time limit is half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.99,0:24:18.73,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,In that time, we have to make something Hattori-san approves of!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.73,0:24:20.10,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Then what about dates?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.10,0:24:21.05,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We won't have that kind of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.05,0:24:23.43,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Right away? Then I'm going to Miho's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.43,0:24:25.44,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Debut and Impatience
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.44,0:24:28.08,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Balancing dreams and love is hard!
